  "title": "CNC Machinist (Turning) #76500",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/Production</li><li>Position Title: <strong>CNC Machinist (Turning)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tuas (Transport provided)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon – Fri: 8.30am – 5.30pm, Sat: 8.30am – 12.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $2200 (Basic) + Allowance + OT + AWS + Variable Bonus (Average Gross $3500/month)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Operate CNC turning machines.</li><li>Set up and adjust machines based on job requirements.</li><li>Read and interpret technical drawings.</li><li>Program basic CNC routines using G codes and M codes.</li><li>Perform maintenance and troubleshooting.</li><li>Inspect finished parts for accuracy.</li><li>Ensure all programs, setups, and tooling lists comply with company Quality System Management (QSM) and Standard Operating Procedures (SOP).</li><li>Perform other duties as required.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Familiarity with Fanuc controls, G codes, and M codes.</li><li>At least 3 years relevant experience.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76500 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
